  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  newborns born in the same hospital

          -  either gender

          -  diagnosis of any pathological/clinical medical condition

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  lack of guardian consent

          -  newborn transferred to/from other hospital

          -  lack of any of the inclusion criteria
      </textblock>
